data.title: Cloudflare Status
data.meta_description: Welcome to Cloudflare's home for real-time and historical data on system performance.
data.text:
About This Site

Cloudflare provides performance and security to website owners via its intelligent global network. This is the system status for the Cloudflare service, both edge network and dashboard/APIs for management.

Status information is also available through Cloudflare Status API here: https://www.cloudflarestatus.com/api.
